Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.52,0:00:04.22,Default,Kyoko,0,0,0,,We were in the same class in 5th and 6th grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.22,0:00:06.76,Default,Kyoko,0,0,0,,We were in the same group because we sat close to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.76,0:00:11.34,Default,Kyoko,0,0,0,,She was quiet, so she didn’t talk to many kids besides me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.34,0:00:14.78,Default,Kyoko,0,0,0,,She was like a sister to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.78,0:00:17.50,Default,Kyoko,0,0,0,,We didn’t play together much, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.50,0:00:22.30,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,When would you say that Lain started to change?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.30,0:00:27.12,Default,Kyoko,0,0,0,,She wasn't so gloomy until about a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.12,0:00:34.48,Default,Kyoko,0,0,0,,When I see her these days, we don’t have much to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.76,0:00:39.12,Default,Kyoko,0,0,0,,It’s too bad, but lately, she’s just another classmate to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.12,0:00:42.46,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Have you talked to her at all recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.46,0:00:48.12,Default,Kyoko,0,0,0,,Recently? I feel like there was something. I wonder what it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.12,0:00:49.46,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Can you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.46,0:00:54.72,Default,Kyoko,0,0,0,,That's weird. I usually have a good memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.72,0:00:57.40,Default,Touko,0,0,0,,Do you remember talking about shopping or boys?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.40,0:01:01.82,Default,Kyoko,0,0,0,,No. I don’t think we talked about that.
